longBusinessSummary: Kakel Max AB (publ) operates in the construction ceramic market in Sweden. The company offers tiles, clinker, and natural stones. It sells its products through its own stores, as well as warehouses and resellers. Kakel Max AB (publ) was founded in 1987 and is based in Östervåla, Sweden.
